      "Text": "Security update for kernel-firmware",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for kernel-firmware fixes the following issues:\n\n- Add microcode_amd_fam17h.bin (bsc#1068032 CVE-2017-5715)\n\nThis new firmware disables branch prediction on AMD family 17h\nprocessor to mitigate an attack on the branch predictor that could\nlead to information disclosure from e.g. kernel memory (bsc#1068032\nCVE-2017-5715).\n\nThis update was imported from the SUSE:SLE-12-SP2:Update update project.",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
